  "description": "A close-up image shows a rusted metal anchor mounted on a light blue surface, likely the hull of a ship. The anchor is heavily corroded with reddish-brown rust, contrasting with the pale blue background. Above the anchor is a circular white plate. The number '7' is painted in yellow next to the plate. Shadowy lines radiate from above, creating a dynamic interplay of light and shadow. Subtle rust streaks extend downwards from the anchor and along the side of the hull. There are white numbers and letters indicating measurements on the hull.",
